snippet: The leader of Libya's Ansar al-sharia militant group in Benghazi warned the United States on Tuesday against interfering in the country's crisis or face worse than their conflicts in Somalia, Iraq, or Afghanistan....

headline.print_headline: Libyan Militant Leader Warns U.S. Against Interference
headline.main: Libyan Militant Leader Warns U.S. Against Interference

lead_paragraph: The leader of Libya's Ansar al-sharia militant group in Benghazi warned the United States on Tuesday against interfering in the country's crisis or face worse than their conflicts in Somalia, Iraq, or Afghanistan.
